title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 15 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Nov 15 2021
description:
Gun charge thrown out in Rittenhouse trial: Size does matter. CNN savages Kamala Harris, who Clay says sounds like she's filling a word quota every time she speaks. Is the media irredeemably dishonest? Yes, Buck notes their alibis are "bull crap." MSBNC -- where Buck declares anything can be racist -- host accuses truck drivers of racism.
